         "description": "<p style=\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\">This upload includes the sample network file, including layout file and uses VISSIM 6.00, 64-bit version to run. A user manual is provided for managing the simulations using manager.py python script and all the prerequisites.<\/p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\">Documentation:<\/p>\r\n<ul style=\"font-size: 12.1599998474121px; line-height: 15.8079996109009px;\">\r\n<li><a href=\"http://ntl.bts.gov/lib/48000/48500/48520/66C294FF.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #0066cc;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Concept of Operations (R.E.S.C.U.M.E.)<\/span><\/span><\/a><\/li>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://ntl.bts.gov/lib/48000/48500/48519/32BFD176.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><span style=\"color: #0066cc;\">Report on Functional and Performance Requirements, and High-Level Data and Communication Needs<\/span><\/span><\/a><\/li>\r\n<li><a href=\"data/repository/DRIVER-ASSISTANCE/RESCUME-CA-IASIM/UserManual.pdf\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #0066cc;\">User Manual<\/span><\/a><\/li>\r\n<li><a href=\"http://ntl.bts.gov/lib/55000/55300/55305/FHWA-JPO-14-137_v1.pdf\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #0066cc;\">Dynamic Mobility Application Policy Analysis: Policy and Institutional Issues for Response, Emergency Staging and Communications, Uniform Management, and Evacuation (R.E.S.C.U.M.E.)Dynamic Mobility Application Policy Analysis: Policy and Institutional Issues for Response, Emergency Staging and Communications, Uniform Management, and Evacuation (R.E.S.C.U.M.E.)<\/span><\/a><\/li>\r\n<\/ul>",
